Visualisations - The World of Imagery

One picture is worth a thousand words. That’s the power of visual imagery. A message which cannot be conveyed through a large set of texts and tabular data can easily be presented through visuals. We often use graphics to make sense of large and complex sets of information. This makes data visualisation a very important step for data understanding.

 

However, to make sense through visuals, it's important to first understand the different types of visuals and their common usage. So let’s dive into the fascinating world of visual imagery.
